item.description:
时长N年半 https://dreamanddead.github.io/post/graphviz-examples/ -<h2 id="usage">usage</h2>
<p>安装相应软件包</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed"><code class="language-text" data-lang="text">$ pacman -S graphviz xdot
</code></pre></div><p>新建 <code>test.dot</code> 文件，保存绘图代码。</p>
<p>使用 xdot 实时预览，</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed"><code class="language-text" data-lang="text">$ xdot test.dot
</code></pre></div><p>绘图结果，生成 png 图片，</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed"><code class="language-text" data-lang="text">$ dot -Tpng -o test.png test.dot
</code></pre></div><h2 id="graph">graph</h2>
<h3 id="undirected">undirected</h3>
<pre><code class="language-dot" data-lang="dot">graph {
label=&quot;Undirected Graph&quot;;
rankdir=LR;
{ rank=same; a, c, d };
splines=line;
a -- b -- c -- e -- a;
a -- c -- d;
}
</code></pre><figure>
<img src="images/undirected-graph.png"/>
</figure>
<h3 id="directed">directed</h3>
<pre><code class="language-dot" data-lang="dot">digraph {
a -&gt; b;
b -&gt; c;
c -&gt; d;
d -&gt; a;
}
</code></pre><figure>
<img src="images/directed-graph.png"/>
</figure>
<h3 id="subgraph">subgraph</h3>
<h4 id="asynomous">asynomous</h4>
<pre><code class="language-dot" data-lang="dot">digraph G {
main -&gt; init -&gt; make_string;
main -&gt; {parse, cleanup};
main -&gt; printf;
parse -&gt; execute -&gt; {make_string, compare, printf};
}
</code></pre><figure>
<img src="images/subgraph.png"/>
</figure>
<h4 id="named">named</h4>
<p>Subgraph name must start with prefix <code>cluster</code>.</p>
<pre><code class="language-dot" data-lang="dot">digraph {
subgraph cluster_0 {
label=&quot;Subgraph A&quot;;
a -&gt; b;
b -&gt; c;
c -&gt; d;
}
subgraph cluster_1 {
label=&quot;Subgraph B&quot;;
a -&gt; f;
f -&gt; c;
}
}
</code></pre><figure>
<img src="images/subgraph-named.png"/>
</figure>
<h2 id="edge">edge</h2>
<h3 id="label">label</h3>
<pre><code class="language-dot" data-lang="dot">digraph {
a -&gt; b[label=&quot;0.2&quot;];
a -&gt; c[label=&quot;0.4&quot;];
c -&gt; b[label=&quot;0.6&quot;];
c -&gt; e[label=&quot;0.6&quot;];
e -&gt; e[label=&quot;0.1&quot;];
e -&gt; b[label=&quot;0.7&quot;];
}
</code></pre><figure>
<img src="images/edge-label.png"/>
</figure>
<h3 id="straight-line">straight line</h3>
<pre><code class="language-dot" data-lang="dot">graph {
splines=line;
subgraph cluster_0 {
label=&quot;Subgraph A&quot;;
a; b; c
}
subgraph cluster_1 {
label=&quot;Subgraph B&quot;;
d; e;
}
a -- e;
a -- d;
b -- d;
b -- e;
c -- d;
c -- e;
}
</code></pre><figure>
<img src="images/edge-straight.png"/>
</figure>
<h2 id="table">table</h2>
<pre><code class="language-dot" data-lang="dot">digraph {
format[label=&lt;
&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;4&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;资产&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt; = &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt; 负债 &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt; + &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;所有者权益&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;现金&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; colspan=&quot;3&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;资本&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;+400,000&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; colspan=&quot;3&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;+400,000&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&gt;, shape=none]
}
</code></pre><figure>
<img src="images/table.png"/>
</figure>
<pre><code class="language-dot" data-lang="dot">digraph {
format[label=&lt;
&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;4&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; colspan=&quot;2&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;现金&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;左边&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;vr/&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;右边&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;现金增加&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;vr/&gt;
&lt;td border=&quot;0&quot; bgcolor=&quot;white&quot;&gt;现金减少&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&gt;, shape=none]
}
</code></pre><figure>
<img src="images/table-hr-vr.png"/>
</figure>
<h2 id="resources">Resources</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.graphviz.org/pdf/dotguide.pdf">dot guide</a>, official manual, precise and clear</li>
